commit.message: Added ReturnTypeWillChange attribute to silence warnings on PHP 8.1
Disable the testRecursive tests, as they cause an incompatibility with PHPUnit 8

Remove default value for arguments

This now shows a deprecation warning in PHP, and, because this never worked
without these arguments filled in any way, it's not a BC break.

Update for recent version of PHPUnit
